R4ng3rNo0b889 is a player spoof who tries to kill the King Black Dragon during a cutscene in A Tail of Two Cats. The cutscene portrays R4ng3rNo0b889 being killed instantly by the dragon, due to the fact that he did not bring an antifire potion or anti-dragon shield to protect himself.

  • R4ng3rNo0b889 being killed by the King Black Dragon's breath.

  • R4ng3rNo0b889 saying "Lolz die noob!"

Trivia[edit | edit source]

  • R4ng3rNo0b is leetspeak for "RangerNoob".
  • It is impossible for this character's username to exist if he were an actual human player, as the limit of all player's names is 12 characters. R4ng3rNo0b889 has 13 in his.
  • He is wearing a Robin Hood hat, black d'hide vambraces, black d'hide body, black d'hide chaps, a magic shortbow, and a pair of ranger boots.
